    <section id="sec-6" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
        6 Parameter-Space Exploration
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        <strong>GMiMC<span class="math">_&#123;\mathrm&#123;crf&#125;&#125;</span>
        vs
        GMiMC<span class="math">_&#123;\mathrm&#123;erf&#125;&#125;</span>.</strong>
        GMiMC<span class="math">_&#123;\mathrm&#123;erf&#125;&#125;</span>
        is always more efficient than
        GMiMC<span class="math">_&#123;\mathrm&#123;crf&#125;&#125;</span>,
