      </p>

      <h3 id="sec-6.1" class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">
        6.1 MPC/SNARK/PQ Signature Applications
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        The two selected GMiMC ciphers are optimized with respect to
        different metrics:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong>SNARK:</strong> minimize total number of operations
          &ndash; case
          <span class="math">\kappa = \log_2 p</span> (using the
