        <li>
          <strong>PQ Signature:</strong> minimize total number of
          multiplications
          <span class="math">\times</span> field size &ndash; case
          <span class="math">\kappa = N</span> in low-data scenario.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>MPC:</strong> minimize/optimize both the total
          number of operations and the total number of (parallel)
          multiplications.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

